Message.MsgText: ODC_InCompleteInfoReceived=ODCF0008I: Partial Routing information was received after waiting for {0} seconds.
Message.Explanation: The Proxy Server has received partial routing information, some information may be missing.
Message.UserResponse: If repeated partial information is received, try increasing the timeout value by setting "routing.info.timeout".

Message.MsgText: ODC_WaitingForInfo=ODCF0006I: Waiting up to {0} seconds to receive routing information.
Message.Explanation: The Proxy is waiting to receive current routing information. The wait will be a timeout in the specified number of seconds.

Message.MsgText: ODC_ServerStartStop=ODCF0009I: Marked server {0} {1} due to transaction: {2}
Message.Explanation: A server has been marked started or stopped in the local ODC tree

Message.MsgText: ODC_AppDeploymentsDirNotFound=ODCF0010W: Unable to read the application deployments directory for {0}.
Message.Explanation: The deployments directory of an application could not be located.
Message.UserResponse: Verify that the application is deployed correctly.

Message.MsgText: ODC_NoWCThreadPool=ODCF0005E: No thread pool is associated with the webcontainer for server {0}.
Message.Explanation: An application server''s web container did not have an associated thread pool.

Message.MsgText: ODC_PluginCfgFileWritten=ODCF0011I: ODC generated plugin-cfg.xml was written to {0}
Message.Explanation: An updated ODC generated plugin-cfg.xml file was written due to events that changed its contents.
The Proxy has received current routing information.

Message.MsgText: ODC_AppNotFound=ODCF0003E: Application {0} not found; ignoring event.
Message.Explanation: An application event was received for a non-existent application.

Message.MsgText: ODC_VHostNotFound=ODCF0004E: Virtual host {0} not found for module {1}.
Message.Explanation: A web module is deployed into a virtual host which was not found.
